          {
            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "fr",
            "value": "Adultes âgés de 16 ans et plus, domiciliés en Gironde et atteints de tumeur cérébrale primitive bénigne ou maligne, dont le diagnostic avait été porté entre le 1er mai 1999 et le 30 avril 2001. "
          },
          {
            "clusion": "I",
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "Adults aged 16 years or more living in Gironde who have malignant or benign primitive brain tumours that were diagnosed between 1st May 1999 and 30th April 2001."
          },
          {
            "clusion": "E",
            "lang": "fr",
            "value": "Les récidives, les tumeurs secondaires, les adénomes hypophysaires, les tumeurs asymptomatiques, de découverte fortuite et les malformations vasculaires ont été exclus de l’étude."
          },
          {
            "clusion": "E",
            "lang": "en",
            "value": "Recurrence, secondary tumours, pituitary adenomas, asymptomatic tumours, incidentally discovered and vascular malformations were excluded from the study."
          }
